frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以穩定黎講，係咪sales 地盤最無解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2250705f4e09aa3e2509a1d723e430d43b72a3e5","tid":228590,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:25:35.000Z","msg":"有幾多人既工作真係可以咁好係自己興趣?<br />\n好少架炸<br />\n工作為錢為生活<br />\n係其他空閒時間 有多餘既錢再發展自己既興趣囉"},{"pid":"82c9c383bdefef30f1c72a0284235997ed38b34d","tid":228590,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:26:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你估真係個個月入幾皮咩大把呀叔中年都係做運輸7仔啦<br />\n<br />\n個個心想事成個社會會好亂<br />\n<br />\n接受現實啦 唔好幻想中年你人工會加好多</blockquote><br />\n咁可能佢地安於現狀無諗法姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就係想轉下行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以穩定黎講，係咪sales 地盤最無解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你學歷唔高，可以點改變呀？記得呢個世界係人簡你，唔係你簡人。"},{"pid":"63f33a1a32690def83dcd26c68a2bf9b73f074c6","tid":228590,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:26:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"281c36ebecd1a954c6edb46de5bf394ccee510ba","tid":228590,"uid":101349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:26:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>手藝？</blockquote><br />\n有乜例子？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入D大工程工司做學徒，或考基電處，做學廚咁Lo...</blockquote><br />\n學廚有諗過，好似叫有門手藝，有多小小想法敢搏學成師又可以開鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然諗到好遠<br />\n不過學廚有乜門路，又唔想讀書灑錢，西餐又好似有型啲"},{"pid":"73dfa8a0c9908aef9fc2d64ec9f85cd859dc7605","tid":228590,"uid":101349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:28:37.000Z","msg":"學歷去到hd仔炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf823434aeafa090ab96fa20a82a5b415cccaa2","tid":228590,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike